Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:04.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(404,370)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:08.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1002,400)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.50,0:01:07.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总共十块九毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:07.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll be 10.95
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.71,0:01:09.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:09.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就放在这边哪里来着的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got it here somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.01,0:01:14.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:14.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.09,0:01:15.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给糖就捣蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:15.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trick or treat
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.34,0:01:18.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是这么付的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:18.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not how this works
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.52,0:01:24.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:24.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My shift is over
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.65,0:01:28.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:28.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.48,0:01:30.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万圣节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:30.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy Halloween
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.28,0:01:35.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看得出来你们俩是要打扮成白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:35.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you're both dressing up as idiots
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来过今年的万圣节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for Halloween this year
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.49,0:01:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可未必
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not quite
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.62,0:01:40.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要打扮成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:40.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going as
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一头海骡子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A sea-mule
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.83,0:01:50.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱俩好像扮的都是屁股这一半
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:50.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we're both rear-ends
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.17,0:01:52.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你自己承认的  别怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:52.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said it, not me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.96,0:01:53.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:53.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.80,0:01:55.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正也用不着上半身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:55.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we don't need a front half
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要在我家过万圣夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're spending the night at my house
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.05,0:01:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发糖果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Giving out candy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.80,0:02:01.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看恐怖片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:01.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And watching scary movies
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,音量开到最大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At full volume
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.93,0:02:05.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:05.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And screaming
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.68,0:02:08.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一整晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:08.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All night long
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.49,0:02:18.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过万圣节光看电影可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:18.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't spend Halloween watching movies
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.78,0:02:21.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须得要有真正的恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:21.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you need is a real scare
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.87,0:02:25.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以  你们得去可怕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:25.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you need to go somewhere scary
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好整晚都待在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And preferably stay there all night
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.21,0:02:30.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要恐怖又空无一人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:30.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somewhere creepy and empty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就比如
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like, um
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:38.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356,580)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.92,0:02:35.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海之霸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:35.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Chum Bucket?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就那里  海之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it, the Chum Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来就没人进去过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one ever goes in there
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.05,0:02:44.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半是因为那里闹鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:44.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe because it's haunted
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.43,0:02:45.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:45.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.97,0:02:48.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海之霸里全是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:48.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Chum Bucket is full of ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.02,0:02:52.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快把自己关进去  天亮之前别出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:52.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now lock yourselves in and don't come out 'til morning
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.77,0:02:53.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:53.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.82,0:02:56.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一定会是史上最棒的万圣节
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:56.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be the best Halloween ever
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.23,0:02:56.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:56.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You wanna come with us?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒挺想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wish I could
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个玩得开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two have fun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(542,798)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.95,0:03:07.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快  趁着没关门躲进去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:07.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, let's hide inside before they close
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.83,0:03:12.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真的闹鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:12.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is haunted
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看也没那么可怕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess it isn't that scary
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:19.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1252,176)}出口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(676,186)}厨房
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人  也可能是有东西过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone or something is coming
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快  躲进厕所里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, let's hide in the bathroom
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我受不了万圣节
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't stand Halloween
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.15,0:03:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来启动防欢乐安保系统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's activate the anti-fun security system
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.24,0:03:42.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免得那些来要糖果的过来敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:42.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before any of those trick or treaters come a-knocking
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最高级别封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maximum lockdown
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,战术监视烟雾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tactical surveillance fog
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  现在关灯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, now hit the lights
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.67,0:03:59.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:03:59.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下不会有谁把这里误认成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one would ever mistake this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过万圣节的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a place to celebrate Halloween
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然不会有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course not
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.01,0:04:08.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都忘了挂骷髅跟南瓜灯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:08.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You forgot the skeletons and jack-o'-lanterns
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要上床睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直有打算要修的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been meaning to fix that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万圣节快乐  亲爱的老公
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy Halloween, honey hubby
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.58,0:04:31.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:31.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.18,0:04:51.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  这里是不是阴森上了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:51.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, did it just get a lot spookier in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要回厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna go back to the bathroom
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能需要开一下灯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we just need some light
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都分不清自己是更紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't decide if I'm m-more nervous
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是更兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or excited
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.66,0:05:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neither can I
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道可以问谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know who we can ask
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.88,0:05:19.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:19.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Chum Bucket?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.17,0:05:24.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:24.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did I--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.88,0:05:25.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们啥时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:25.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When did you--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我们现在这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, do we seem
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是更紧张还是更兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,more nervous or excited?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们样子像白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You seem like morons
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a relief
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要闪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm leaving
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And do not follow me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:45.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1452,194)}出口
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门好像锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think the doors are locked
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢尔顿  入侵者警报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sheldon, intruder alert
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那群来过万圣节的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those Halloween hooligans
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.67,0:06:01.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:01.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lemme see 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.59,0:06:07.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好兴奋能来废弃的海之霸过万圣夜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited to be spending Halloween night
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the old abandoned Chum Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.05,0:06:11.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟好朋友派大星跟章鱼哥找魑魅魍魉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,looking for ghosts and ghouls
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with my best friends Patrick and Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.47,0:06:18.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个白痴还真会带朋友来这过万圣节
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:15.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That soft-headed sap
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would bring his friends here for Halloween
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然他们想要恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if it's a scare they want
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.44,0:06:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就吓死他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then I'll scare them to death
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的小鬼头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My little ghoul
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.74,0:06:37.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算有点万圣节的精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:37.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is finally getting into the Halloween spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:48.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(488,138)}厨房
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.71,0:06:48.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好  这扇门也锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:48.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wonderful, this one's locked too
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.18,0:06:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听说用过这个纸巾盒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I heard this napkin dispenser was used by a guy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who disappeared
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.31,0:06:59.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听说这盐瓶还有胡椒瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:59.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I heard these salt and pepper shakers
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面其实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are actually
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,装的是其他调料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,some other seasoning
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.69,0:07:06.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听说从前有这两个傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:06.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I heard one time these two imbeciles
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害得我整晚被反锁在海之霸里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,locked me in the Chum Bucket all night
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.95,0:07:14.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:14.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stupid
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.67,0:07:22.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:22.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,punks
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海之霸还真的闹鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Chum Bucket really is haunted
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边那扇门好像开着的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, that door looks open
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.65,0:07:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们跑我地下实验室去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They went down into my basement lab
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.70,0:07:53.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下我可真能吓吓他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:53.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I can really scare them
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.83,0:08:01.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:01.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摸黑找找电灯开关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feel around for a light switch
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像找到了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I found one
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好大一盏台灯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a big lamp
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是很黑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's still pretty dark
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别的也打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's turn on these other ones
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.85,0:08:20.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  也许不应该
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:20.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, maybe we shouldn't--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.71,0:08:49.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:49.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我不怎么怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm much less scared now
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.34,0:08:56.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们激怒了海之霸的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:56.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have angered the spirits of the Chum Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.01,0:08:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你们的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now your souls
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就要归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will be mine
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看招  你个吸血鬼德古拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take this, you Dracula
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些失灵的机器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those malfunctioning machines
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.72,0:09:39.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打开了某种幽灵通道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:39.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are opening up some kind of spectral gateway
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.77,0:09:48.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们为什么会打扮成牛仔的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:48.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are they dressed like cowboys?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海之霸可是我低价买来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I bought the Chum Bucket cheap
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.57,0:09:55.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为它一开始建在古代牛仔墓地上边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because it was built
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:55.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on an ancient cowboy burial ground
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.57,0:10:02.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而这墓地又建在宠物公墓上边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:02.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which was built on top of a pet cemetery
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再加上沉船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a shipwreck
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.55,0:10:17.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再加上史前焦油坑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:17.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a prehistoric tar pit
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.38,0:10:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还能怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can I say?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱贪便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love a good deal
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,红辣椒粉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Paprika
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.42,0:10:55.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肉豆蔻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:55.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nutmeg
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.69,0:11:21.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你过万圣节简直是拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:21.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you sure go all out for Halloween
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少我们在外面挺安全的  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least we're safe out here, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.54,0:11:30.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:30.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,908)}未完待续
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给糖就捣蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trick or treat
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.91,0:12:08.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蛋好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:08.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Egg-scuse us
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.63,0:12:22.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些烦人鬼滚出我餐厅了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:22.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those pesky poltergeists are out of my restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要回去睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welp, I'm going back to bed
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.51,0:12:30.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能让比奇堡一直这么闹鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:30.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't let Bikini Bottom stay haunted
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.14,0:12:32.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天可是万圣节
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:32.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Halloween
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都爱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They love it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do not love this
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.98,0:12:39.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:39.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.03,0:12:42.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道可以用什么说服你来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:42.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what'll convince you to help
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A song
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.66,0:12:47.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:47.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, fine
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.87,0:12:55.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要你不唱歌  我就去把幽灵抓回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:55.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get the ghosts back as long as you don't sing
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万圣节本来就够恐怖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Halloween is scary enough
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.55,0:13:02.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:02.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个工业级幽灵吸尘器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One industrial ghost vacuum
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听候差遣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at your service
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.51,0:13:10.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就需要个东西来收纳那群幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:10.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All we need now is something to contain those ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.18,0:13:14.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要方方黄黄伸缩自如的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:14.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something absorbent yet porous
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定这样安全吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're sure this is safe?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大概不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Probably not
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甚至可能会要你命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It might even kill you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要按按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna push the button
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,660)}停
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.69,0:14:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就只要摧毁他的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now all we have to do is destroy his body
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.03,0:14:09.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这闹鬼问题就能彻底解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:09.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and this ghost problem will be solved for good
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Silence
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.37,0:14:21.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们诸多亡魂已经愤怒了上千年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:21.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We spirits have been angry for millennia
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And do you know why?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.75,0:14:25.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为今天是万圣节
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:25.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because it's Halloween
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们从来没要过糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you've never been trick-or-treating?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's our
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未了的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,unfinished business
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说只要带他们去要糖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So we just have to take them all trick-or-treating
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.35,0:14:38.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们就会离开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:38.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and they'll go away?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们说怎么样呢  幽灵们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you say, ghosts?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, matey
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就让这些幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then let's give these ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.11,0:14:52.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过上他们来世最美好的万圣节吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:52.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the best Halloween of their afterlives
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(738,458)}肯尼阿猫
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.92,0:15:03.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给糖就捣蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:03.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trick or treat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶油硬糖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Butterscotch
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yum
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.00,0:15:46.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们让这次万圣节好玩到要我们命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:46.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have made this a Halloween to die for
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,again
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.84,0:15:54.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们终于可以安息了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:54.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we can finally be at peace
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再次感谢  搭档们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks again, partners
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.61,0:16:11.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:11.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.45,0:16:16.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:16.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aww, man
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.12,0:16:20.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下得重新要一遍糖了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:20.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we have to trick-or-treat all over again
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait for me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别让我多花一分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't make me spend another minute
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.63,0:16:25.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陪着这些白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:25.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with these idiots
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.92,0:16:27.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:27.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(780,876)}快去捡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(670,544)\frz19.46}编剧{\fnArial}/{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}导演
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:39.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.46\pos(676,548)}{\fnArial}CG{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}动画制作公司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:36.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.46\pos(742,304)}美术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:36.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.46\pos(768,728)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:37.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.46\pos(694,478)}统筹
