Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.46\pos(634,552)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1354,622)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.60,0:16:43.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:43.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.73,0:16:45.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:45.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快捡回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring it on home
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,G-A-R-Y
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不需要靠空气活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He don't need no air supply
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.78,0:16:51.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:51.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.44,0:16:52.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:52.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.86,0:16:55.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四十五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:55.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forty-five minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破你最快时间记录了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your fastest time yet
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这球我们拥有了一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've had this ball forever
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我依然记得自己最初把球给你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I still remember when I first gave it to you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:12.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(398,854)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是颗球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a ball
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  这次投球我要加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, Gary, I'm gonna put a little pepper on this pitch
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做到了  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did it, Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我踢到球了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I kicked the ball
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.58,0:17:40.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:40.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.29,0:17:45.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗的球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:45.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary's ball
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个字都不用再说  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't say another word, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know just what you're thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.84,0:17:52.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要跳进那个海沟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:52.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are gonna jump down into that trench
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捡回你的友谊之球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and get your friendship ball back
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.63,0:17:57.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至死方休
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:57.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or we're gonna die trying
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.64,0:18:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna die
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.02,0:18:07.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还好有这一大堆遗失的球垫着做缓冲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:07.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thing this huge pile of lost balls broke our fall
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.65,0:18:15.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么在这么大一堆球里找到我们的球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:15.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are we gonna find our ball in this giant pile?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.82,0:18:18.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来它就掉在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:18.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was just sitting here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.74,0:18:21.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这堆被咬过的可怕骨头堆上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:21.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on this gruesome mound of gnawed bones
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我们不是故意要碰你骨头的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we didn't mean to touch your bones
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是在找我们那颗特别的友谊之球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We were just looking for our special friendship ball
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然友谊之球找回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that we've got our friendship ball back
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.39,0:18:45.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会再放开它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:45.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm never letting it go again
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.48,0:18:49.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说过  我绝对不会再放开这颗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:49.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I'm never letting go of this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ball
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不算太糟嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this isn't so bad
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑远点去接  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go long, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.76,0:20:01.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你马上就能得救了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:01.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're as good as rescued, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.69,0:20:15.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:15.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.93,0:21:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它长得好像章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That looks like Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our ball
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.73,0:21:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.65,0:21:46.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们简直天下无
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:46.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are truly invincib--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.36,0:21:48.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:48.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,G-Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.62,0:21:49.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:49.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.49,0:21:49.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丢给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:49.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Throw you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.28,0:21:50.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这颗球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:50.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The ball
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.58,0:21:52.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:52.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.70,0:21:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没法拖住它多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hold her back much longer
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.16,0:21:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Save
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.25,0:21:58.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:58.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.02,0:22:17.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  为什么要放弃你的球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:17.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, why did you give up your ball?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.19,0:22:20.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说这球只是个玩具是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:20.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean the ball was just a toy?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.23,0:22:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们创造的回忆才重要  球并不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the memories we made that matter, not the ball?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可以玩这颗新球来创造新的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we can make new memories with this new ball?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.78,0:22:34.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你好聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:34.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, you are so wise
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.24,0:22:35.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:35.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get over here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.87,0:22:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做到了  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did it, Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.17,0:22:41.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又踢到球了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:41.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I kicked the ball again
